entries.journal_entry_description: The Empire is bringing their Dark Troopers to assist in Restuss. Hunt them down and defeat them before they even reach Restuss. Note: Only enemies designated exactly as 'Dark Trooper' will count toward mission completion.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You've been tasked with defeating 5 Dark Troopers of the Imperial Army.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Lieutenant Olvog in Restuss and let him know that your assignment is done.
